<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>الواو <span style="color:#947721">{مِنْ وَلِيٍّ}</span>، <span style="color:#947721">{سِراجاً وَهّاجاً}</span>.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>الميم <span style="color:#947721">{مِنْ ماءٍ}</span>، <span style="color:#947721">{صِراطٍ مُسْتَقِيمٍ}</span>.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
